00:35:18.466 --> 00:35:22.186
years. And later last year, we have this

594
00:35:22.326 --> 00:35:25.766
uniformed funding strategy at the entire

595
00:35:25.906 --> 00:35:29.846
NIH where the pay line is removed. So

596
00:35:29.906 --> 00:35:33.726
now we are looking at multiple factors, and most importantly,

597
00:35:34.206 --> 00:35:38.066
it's the institute priorities. However, peer review, as

